運輸之舟、\r\n    車、航空機內而犯之。\r\n前項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/111%2c%e6%98%93%2c120%2c20220307%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,111,易,120,20220307,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"易","JNO":"120","JDATE":"20220307","JTITLE":"加重竊盜等"}